{
  "stem": "6719.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I pick up a little pouch, a little velvet pouch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It couldn't have been bigger than about that, maybe six inches, five inches, with a little string on there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I open it up-- and just to predicate this statement, at the one end of the barracks where we broke open the suitcases, there was a big wooden box down there with two handles.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every piece of jewelry, monies, anything that was of value had to be dumped in down there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The clothing, the chemises, the panties, the who knows what, the blankets-- everybody brought a blanket anyhow-- were put inside down there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they were brought over to the girls', to the women's barrack down there, where they had to catalog it and put it so it had to be sent to Germany if it was clean and all that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I opened that little pouch and I put it on my hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were two rings down there with some stones in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know, some red stones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a small bracelet with a few stones in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I want to take this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm going to put it into that, into that box.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, Hans says to me, says [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just give it to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll throw it in down there, OK?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I give it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just as much as I observed what happened outside crematorium five in 1944, it's like having eyes in the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw that he did not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He walked toward that, but he never dropped it in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw him putting it in his tunic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That evening, when roll call-- again, the roll-- all roll call was always there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were counted again in fives.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
